article_id:216,category_name:Maintenance,title_name:Forced Exit Maintenance on 1/29(JST) [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We will be performing maintenance during the period noted below. When the maintenance begins, the game will be closed automatically. This maintenance is to adjust the specifications for summoning and getherwings.</div><div>・Please remember to collect the daily reward from the 30-Day Pack (Recovery) before maintenance begins.</div><div><br></div><div>■Maintenance period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548727200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548745200"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Regarding the forced exit</div><div>1. If the maintenance starts while you are playing a quest, the game will automatically exit. You will not receive any rewards that dropped up to that point. Stamina and getherwings will not be expended.</div><div>2. If the maintenance starts while you are playing a quest, even if you resume play after the maintenance is over, the game will automatically exit once the game communicates with the server, such as when moving between areas. You will not receive any rewards that dropped up to that point. Stamina and getherwings will not be expended.</div><div><br></div><div>■Details</div><div>1. Players will now be guaranteed a 5★ adventurer when performing the initial tutorial summon after creating game data for the first time.</div><div>After this maintenance is complete, we will send one 5★ Summon Voucher to all players who created game data and performed the initial summon by <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548727200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>This notice will be modified after they&rsquo;ve been distributed.</div><div><br></div><div>2. Players will now be able to participate in co-op without expending stamina by using getherwings. Hosts will now use getherwings instead of stamina when playing co-op quests.</div><div><br></div><div>3. The Getherwing cost of the following quests will be reduced from 3 to 2 for all elements:</div><div>・Dragon Trials: Master</div><div>・Imperial Onslaught: Master</div><div>・Imperial Onslaught: Expert</div><div><br></div><div>■Notes</div><div>1. The game will be inaccessible during maintenance.</div><div>2. A 5★ Summon Voucher will not be sent to players who create game data after <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548745200"></span>.</div><div>3. Maintenance may start and/or end before or after the scheduled times.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548745500"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>The maintenance was completed on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548745200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>We will send one 5★ Summon Voucher to all players who have already performed the initial summon after creating game data. This notice will be modified after they&rsquo;ve been distributed.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548762600"></span>]</strong></span><br>As a token of our gratitude for your patience during the maintenance, we have sent the following gift to players who started the game before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548727200"></span>.<br><br>・Wyrmite x500<br>・Quality Honey x10<br>・Blessed Ethon Ashes x10<br><br>We are still preparing to send the 5★ Summon Voucher.<br>There will be an addendum in this news once it is sent.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548770100"></span>]</strong></span><br>We have sent the following gift to layers who have performed the initial summon after creating game data by <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1548727200"></span>.<br><br>・5★ Summon Voucher x1<br><br>This will be sent to your goodies box when you log in, and you can claim it until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1549346340"></span>. This is seven days after it&#39;s sent to your goodie box.<br>&nbsp;</div><div>■ About 5★ Summon Vouchers:</div><div>・ The 5★ adventurers summonable using the 5★ Summon Voucher are those displayed under 5★ Adventurer Summon Rates for the 5★ Summon Voucher in the Welcome Pack at the time of use.</div><div>・ Limited-time 5★ adventurers are not included in the list of adventurers that can be summoned using 5★ Summon Vouchers.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1548136800,update_time1549535415